DataElement.preferredName: Regulation Submission Assessment Expected Resubmission Date and Time ISO21090.TS.DATETIME.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: The date on which the resubmission of the regulatory application is expected. NOTE(S): Used only when RegulatoryAssessment.statusCode is not complete. Regulatory authorities typically assign a resubmission deadline such as 30 days.
